              "text": "Hotel where people have thought of everything. The complete picture is correct to small details such as shoehorns, slippers,..... We stayed in the Corniche suite. Spacious room with views of the Nile. Soundproofed rooms. Nicely finished. The staff is very friendly and helpful. We also ate at restaurant 8, the Lebanese restaurant and the Italian restaurant. All 3 good of its kind. Breakfast is provided with all options. In short, highly recommended.",
