            {
              "id": 1052677975,
              "helpfulVotes": 1,
              "rating": 5,
              "title": "Four Seasons Nile Plaza , Cairo, Egypt and  Mr. Kamal Walid",
              "text": "After a full day at the Egyptian  Museum we stopped into the Four  Seasons hoping to find a table for dinner. We met Mr. Kamal Walid at the Concierge Desk who accompanied my wife and I to several of the hotels' restaurants  searching for a table until he could finally procure us a table at the poolside restaurant and bar where we enjoyed a lovely meal and service.  \nOur experience was incredible because of Mr. Walid.  He is an astounding gentleman and representative o The Four Seasons, a true asset to the hotel.  Because of him we would book our next stay in Cairo at The Four Seasons.",
              "status": "PUBLISHED",
              "tripInfo": {
                "stayDate": "2026-03-31",
                "tripType": "FAMILY"
              },
              "location": {
                "name": "Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza",
                "locationId": 308077,
                "parentGeoId": 294201,
                "absoluteUrl": "https://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g294201-d308077-Reviews-Four_Seasons_Hotel_Cairo_at_Nile_Plaza-Cairo_Cairo_Governorate.html"
              },
              "locationId": 308077,
              "publishedDate": "2026-03-11",
              "ownerResponseId": 1053057485,
              "ownerResponse": {
                "id": 1053057485,
                "text": "Dear Sharon, \n\nThank you for sharing such a wonderful account of your visit. It truly warms our hearts to know that your evening after the Egyptian Museum became even more memorable.\nMr. Walid embodies the spirit of genuine care that guides everything we do, and your kind words will mean so much to him. We’re delighted that he was able to accompany you personally and ensure you found the perfect spot to enjoy your dinner by the pool. Moments like these are exactly what we hope to create for every guest who walks through our doors.\nWe would be honored to welcome you for a future stay, and we look forward to the opportunity to craft even more special experiences during your next visit to Cairo.\n\nKind regards,\nYves Giacometti\nRegional Vice President and General Manager\nFour Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza",
                "publishedDate": "2026-03-15",
