            {
              "id": 1051568421,
              "helpfulVotes": 0,
              "rating": 5,
              "title": "Impeccable Service in fabulous surroundings",
              "text": "A Truly World Class Hotel located ideally in Cairo.  I can’t recommend this hotel enough.  One of the finest I’ve visited anywhere in the World.  Staff went out of their way to assist.  I emailed a request through in English and Salma Ahmad answered swiftly enabling my wishes and everything was arranged with style and elegance.  If you are looking for the best hotel in Cairo…  Stay here.",
              "status": "PUBLISHED",
              "tripInfo": {
                "stayDate": "2026-03-31",
                "tripType": "COUPLES"
              },
              "location": {
                "name": "Four Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza",
                "locationId": 308077,
                "parentGeoId": 294201,
                "absoluteUrl": "https://www.tripadvisor.com/Hotel_Review-g294201-d308077-Reviews-Four_Seasons_Hotel_Cairo_at_Nile_Plaza-Cairo_Cairo_Governorate.html"
              },
              "locationId": 308077,
              "publishedDate": "2026-03-01",
              "ownerResponseId": 1053058048,
              "ownerResponse": {
                "id": 1053058048,
                "text": "Dear Lee, \n\nThank you for taking the time to share such a wonderful review. It’s truly heartening to know that your experience with us stood out as one of the finest you’ve had anywhere in the world — this is exactly the level of care and craftsmanship we aspire to deliver.\nI’m especially delighted to hear about your interaction with Salma. She embodies the genuine warmth and dedication our team takes pride in, and I know she will be thrilled to learn how much her thoughtful assistance enhanced your stay. Ensuring your requests were handled with elegance and ease is at the core of our service promise.\n\nWe are honoured by your recommendation and grateful for your kind words about our location, surroundings, and overall atmosphere. It would be our pleasure to welcome you back for many more memorable visits to Cairo.\n\nKind regards,\nYves Giacometti\nRegional Vice President and General Manager\nFour Seasons Hotel Cairo at Nile Plaza",
                "publishedDate": "2026-03-15",
